 "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031327_944232693629964_9170031439955477455_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cEarR9ILeocQ7kNvgE3-wst&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBLu_AIVGtUaQ1KgrfDCyzMJbsyvDPnV8sbAOmY0lkpig&oe=66D44007"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Mini Games", "keywords": [], "long_description": "A collection of seated mini games including:\n\nRail Targets: Hit the targets, while riding in a rail carriage.\n\nPiece Puzzle: Connect the pieces of an object to complete the puzzle.\n\nUnblock The Road: Slide the blocks to connect the road.\n\nMinesweeper: Find all the mines and clear the grid.\n\nShell Game: Pick which cup the ball is in, after the cups have been moved around.\n\nKlondike Solitaire: The classic game of Klondike using playing cards.\n\nPyramid Solitaire: The classic card game where you have to find pairs that add up to 13.\n\nSpider Solitaire: A popular variation of solitaire with the option to play with either 1 suit or 2 suits, for increased difficulty.\n\nJigsaw Puzzle: Choose a picture and complete the puzzle.\n\nChess: The classic game of chess.\n\nCheckers: The classic game of checkers.\n\nWhack A Mole: Hit as many moles as you can, as fast as you can.\n\nWire Loop Game: Move the hoop along the wire, within the time limit.\n\nShooting Gallery: Get as many points as you can, by shooting the objects.\n\nMarble Solitaire: Complete the game by removing all the balls, but one, from the board.\n\nCarnival Rail: Throw baseballs and hoops at the carnival style targets, while riding in a rail carriage.", "short_description": "A collection of seated mini games:\n\nRail Targets: Hit the targets riding a carriage.\nPiece Puzzle: Connect the pieces.\nUnblock The Road: Slide the blocks.\nMinesweeper\nShell Game: Which cup is the ball in?\nKlondike Solitaire\nPyramid Solitaire\nSpider Solitaire\nJigsaw Puzzle: Complete the puzzle.\nChess\nCheckers\nWhack A Mole\nWire Loop Game: Move the hoop along the wire.\nShooting Gallery: Get as many points as you can.\nMarble Solitaire\nCarnival Rail: Throw baseballs and hoops, riding in a carriage."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://mobilefusionapps.com/privacypolicyvr.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "MobileFusion Apps LTD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://mobilefusionapps.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["CASUAL", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "824079182735454"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75367591_935546914479423_293927678659637453_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WpHYUNvQhJUQ7kNvgHzqVMI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBsK8eyIa24jwehfn5i06XtMHhIVx4dfHdjCfJLm2FVCQ&oe=66D4434E"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Mini Games", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "release_date": 1641081600, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "4831675176856143", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "4440362002746502", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": 